ActYukon Act
SubjectAdministration and Control of the Public Lands - Yukon ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder (1) approving the relinquisment, as relinquised by Yukon Order in Council 2010/139 of the administration and control from the Commissioner of YUKON to Her Majesty in Right of Canada, in perpetuity, of a laneway a public real property located under the Elijah Smith Building at 300 Main Street in the City of Whitehorse, Yukon; and (2) identifiying the Minister of Public Works and Government Services as the Federal Minister who will have the administration of that laneway.
